statements: SELECT * FROM GreenBuildingAssessments
SELECT development_name, assessment_date FROM GreenBuildingAssessments
SELECT assessment_id, development_name, total_impact_score FROM GreenBuildingAssessments
SELECT * FROM GreenBuildingAssessments WHERE total_impact_score > 50
SELECT development_name, assessment_date FROM GreenBuildingAssessments WHERE assessment_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31'
SELECT * FROM GreenBuildingAssessments WHERE total_impact_score > 80 ORDER BY assessment_date DESC;
SELECT development_name, assessment_date FROM GreenBuildingAssessments WHERE assessment_date BETWEEN '2020-01-01' AND '2021-01-01' ORDER BY development_name ASC;

SELECT development_name, MAX(total_impact_score) AS highest_score FROM GreenBuildingAssessments GROUP BY development_name;
SELECT assessment_date, SUM(total_impact_score) AS total_score FROM GreenBuildingAssessments GROUP BY assessment_date HAVING total_score > 200;
